### [Genesis Chapter 27](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#001.md)

[Genesis](../../../bib/kjv/gen001.htm#001.md)

<span class="margnote"><span id="an_000">gen 27:0</span></span>

Overview

[Gen 27:1](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#001.md), Isaac sends Esau for
venison; [Gen 27:6](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#006.md), Rebekah instructs
Jacob to obtain the blessing; [Gen
27:14](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#014.md), Jacob, feigning to be Esau,
obtains it; [Gen 27:30](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#030.md), Esau brings
venison; [Gen 27:33](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#033.md), Isaac trembles;
[Gen 27:34](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#034.md), Esau complains, and by
importunity obtains a blessing; [Gen
27:41](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#041.md), He threatens Jacob's life; [Gen
27:42](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#042.md), Rebekah disappoints him, by
sending Jacob away.

