<span class="margnote"><span id="an_016">gen 27:16</span></span>

skins: Travellers inform us, that the Eastern goats have long, fine, and
beautiful hair, of the most delicate silky softness; indeed the animals
generally in those hot countries are not covered with so thick a coat of
hair as they are in more northerly regions; so that Isaac might easily
be deceived, when his eyes were dim, and his feeling no less impaired
than his sight. [Gen 27:16](../../../bib/kjv/gen027.htm#016.md)

